instance0   allow-local          import                                                                      accept       
instance0   peer0-ipv4-PodCIDR   export   fd00:10:99:7::1                    10.244.0.0/24 (24..24)          accept       
instance0   peer0-ipv6-PodCIDR   export   fd00:10:99:7::1                    fd00:10:244::/64 (64..64)       accept       
instance0   peer1-ipv4-PodCIDR   export   fd00:10:99:7::2                    10.244.0.0/24 (24..24)          accept       
instance0   peer1-ipv6-PodCIDR   export   fd00:10:99:7::2                    fd00:10:244::/64 (64..64)       accept       
instance1   allow-local          import                                                                      accept       
instance1   peer0-ipv4-PodCIDR   export   fd00:10:99:7::3                    10.244.0.0/24 (24..24)          accept       
instance1   peer0-ipv6-PodCIDR   export   fd00:10:99:7::3                    fd00:10:244::/64 (64..64)       accept       
instance1   peer1-ipv4-PodCIDR   export   fd00:10:99:7::4                    10.244.0.0/24 (24..24)          accept       
instance1   peer1-ipv6-PodCIDR   export   fd00:10:99:7::4                    fd00:10:244::/64 (64..64)       accept       
