Instance    Peer    Prefix          NextHop           Age
instance0   peer0   10.244.0.0/24   fd00:10:99:7::5   -
            peer1   10.244.0.0/24   fd00:10:99:7::5   -
instance1   peer0   10.244.0.0/24   fd00:10:99:7::6   -
            peer1   10.244.0.0/24   fd00:10:99:7::6   -
