Instance    Peer    Prefix             NextHop           Age
instance0   peer0   fd00:10:244::/64   fd00:10:99:7::5   -
            peer1   fd00:10:244::/64   fd00:10:99:7::5   -
instance1   peer0   fd00:10:244::/64   fd00:10:99:7::6   -
            peer1   fd00:10:244::/64   fd00:10:99:7::6   -
