instance0   peer0   10.0.0.0/24   fd00:10:99:7::1   -
            peer1   10.0.0.0/24   fd00:10:99:7::2   -
instance1   peer0   10.0.1.0/24   fd00:10:99:7::3   -
            peer1   10.0.2.0/24   fd00:10:99:7::4   -
